  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/af9e13c34865023e221928614c55d074.poster.avif?t=1668799122\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/af9e13c34865023e221928614c55d074.webm?t=1668799122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/af9e13c34865023e221928614c55d074.mp4?t=1668799122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Metagalactic Blitz is a sci-fi dodgeball brawler. Choose your fighter, grab a ball and blast your opponents away in this competitive online arena game.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/d545d6524146a2651415be65d6da6ddb.webp?t=1668799122\" width=617 height=48 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\t<li>Deep dodgeball mechanics that encourage strategic gameplay<br>\t</li><li>9 characters with entirely different playstyles<br>\t</li><li>5 arenas with unique mechanics<br>\t</li><li>1v1 online multiplayer<br>\t</li><li>Online ranked matchmaking<br>\t</li><li>1-4 player local multiplayer<br>\t</li><li>Original soundtrack by 8 Bit Cypher</li></ul><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/1c1b5b1065c00fc193f5609136d06456.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/f4ec543cb10a043e5a18b4f51ea42604.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=159 /></span><br>Zomborg is a slow bruiser, excelling at guarding the middle and soaking up damage.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/c3b7b20ad998ae3f9520102515d9eabd.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=174 /></span><br>Lt. Justice has fantastic tools for overwhelming, constantly hurling his boomerang shield and backing you into a gravity bomb to set up for a kill.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/e33a3e7554e910966ce7e3fd6c097fde.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=172 /></span><br>Maxameleon gains the advantage slowly but surely. He can negate attacks while outliving his opponent as they weaken from his poison.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/d892289786309125d93181a6da63fc46.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=174 /></span><br>To master Zandra, perfect spacing is a must. The tip of her sword is especially deadly; swift and accurate combos allow Zandra to dominate the arena.<br><br><br><br>Discover more characters in game!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/f1a8494825f4e6729531c7a92526e898.webp?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=48 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/4e88913dc534d01b9969410221aab5d0.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br>An abandoned rebel mining operation turned dodgeball arena. This map has more space than usual, but targeting the crystals in the back will cause a section of your opponent’s stage to collapse.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/a82ef8497aad50dde06b1ba4354dc941.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br>Battle it out in the urban district! This arena features tug-of-war style gameplay. Gain ground by pushing your opponent to the edge.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/e01609f627d6e4c95969c95e4c56ffdd.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br>A remote alien planet with dodgeball-loving natives. Compete for control of the throwable crystals that they toss out, each having an special on-hit effect.<br><br><br>And more in game!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/af9e13c34865023e221928614c55d074.poster.avif?t=1668799122\" width=628 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/af9e13c34865023e221928614c55d074.webm?t=1668799122\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/af9e13c34865023e221928614c55d074.mp4?t=1668799122\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Metagalactic Blitz is a sci-fi dodgeball brawler. Choose your fighter, grab a ball and blast your opponents away in this competitive online arena game.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/d545d6524146a2651415be65d6da6ddb.webp?t=1668799122\" width=617 height=48 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\t<li>Deep dodgeball mechanics that encourage strategic gameplay<br>\t</li><li>9 characters with entirely different playstyles<br>\t</li><li>5 arenas with unique mechanics<br>\t</li><li>1v1 online multiplayer<br>\t</li><li>Online ranked matchmaking<br>\t</li><li>1-4 player local multiplayer<br>\t</li><li>Original soundtrack by 8 Bit Cypher</li></ul><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/1c1b5b1065c00fc193f5609136d06456.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=137 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/f4ec543cb10a043e5a18b4f51ea42604.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=159 /></span><br>Zomborg is a slow bruiser, excelling at guarding the middle and soaking up damage.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/c3b7b20ad998ae3f9520102515d9eabd.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=174 /></span><br>Lt. Justice has fantastic tools for overwhelming, constantly hurling his boomerang shield and backing you into a gravity bomb to set up for a kill.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/e33a3e7554e910966ce7e3fd6c097fde.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=172 /></span><br>Maxameleon gains the advantage slowly but surely. He can negate attacks while outliving his opponent as they weaken from his poison.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/d892289786309125d93181a6da63fc46.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=174 /></span><br>To master Zandra, perfect spacing is a must. The tip of her sword is especially deadly; swift and accurate combos allow Zandra to dominate the arena.<br><br><br><br>Discover more characters in game!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/f1a8494825f4e6729531c7a92526e898.webp?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=48 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/4e88913dc534d01b9969410221aab5d0.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br>An abandoned rebel mining operation turned dodgeball arena. This map has more space than usual, but targeting the crystals in the back will cause a section of your opponent’s stage to collapse.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/a82ef8497aad50dde06b1ba4354dc941.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br>Battle it out in the urban district! This arena features tug-of-war style gameplay. Gain ground by pushing your opponent to the edge.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/564080/extras/e01609f627d6e4c95969c95e4c56ffdd.avif?t=1668799122\" width=616 height=308 /></span><br>A remote alien planet with dodgeball-loving natives. Compete for control of the throwable crystals that they toss out, each having an special on-hit effect.<br><br><br>And more in game!",
